Author: rail
Name: AetherDraw
Punchline: A realtime multi-user whiteboard raid planner
Description: A realtime multi-user whiteboard raid planner to draw strategy images for encounters. Use /aetherdraw to open. Supports aetherdraw.me users, external url plan imports.
Changelog:
v2.4.2.0: Overhauled Load/Import window with tabs. Added ability to 'Append' plans (merge pages) from files or URLs. Replaced old Load popup.
v2.4.1.0: Added Community Plan Browser (Search & Load).
v2.4.0.0: Added Status Icon search, per-page undo, page re-ordering, and live property editing.
